 Actress Lala Akindoju And Husband Chef Fregz Expecting Their First Child Nollywood actress Lala Akindoju and her popular chef husband, Gbubemi Fregene, better known as Chef Fregz are expecting their first child and pregnancy really looks good on her as she glows as ever. Sharing the good news on her Instagram page, Lala Akindoju said they are on their way to becoming 3 members of the family. She captioned the photos; “…becoming three”. Chef Fregz also shared a black and white photo of Lala’s baby bump, with the caption, “The Evolution???”. They got married in Lagos, Nigeria in 2018. The couple celebrated their second wedding anniversary on September 20.